The national seat is located in Alcobendas, Madrid.
There, more than a hundred technicians (generally mechanical experts) work simultaneously on three computer screens.
Audex invests 90 million each year to develop these databases.
Each month, 2.5 million data are recorded, and customers receive updates every two days.
The development of this huge flow of information allows these companies to give them different uses and offer different products.
The most common application concerns repair and maintenance, but according to countries, there are also tools for the management of parts or to calculate the venous or residual value of a car.
